</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
{{TitleProperty|SketchOnSurface}}
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* {{PropertyData|Extra Objects|LinkList}}: Additional objects that will be mapped on surface
